import { TextField } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

export default function Edit({post}) {
  return (
    <StyledTableRow>
        <StyledTableCell>
          <TextField 
          required
          value='{post.title}'
          name='title'></TextField>
        </StyledTableCell>
        <StyledTableCell>
        <TextField 
          required
          value='{post.body}'
          name='body'></TextField>
        </StyledTableCell>
    </StyledTableRow>
  )
}
